status R
description Auroral intensity modelling using radar measurments and multi-spectral imaging
contact Sam Tuttle
email sat1e10@soton.ac.uk
operator EISCAT staff
submitter Sam Tuttle
resources PP(16)
notes
We will use single-station multi-spectral imaging in conjunction with radar
measurements to model the intensity of small-scale aurora in the magnetic zenith.

arc_slice program to be run
